LogicalTable.name: Fact Compound - Account Transactions Time Series

LogicalColumn.name: Chg 2 Months Ago # TXNs
LogicalColumn.Description: This column calculates the change between the # of Transactions on all accounts of the customer that were incurred 2 Months ago and 1 month ago.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: IFNULL("%1", 0) - IFNULL("%2", 0)
Expr.ExprTextDesc: IFNULL("Core"."Fact - CRM - Account Transaction Last 6 Months"."# TXNs 1 Month Ago", 0) - IFNULL("Core"."Fact - CRM - Account Transaction Last 6 Months"."# TXNs 2 Months Ago", 0)

LogicalColumn.name: % Chg 2 Months Ago # TXNs

Expr.name: Expr
